{"tid":2208246,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府回應陳方安生「以法而治」：貶低港法治聲譽言論對發展無益","createTime":"2020-09-18T17:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T18:04:53.000Z","uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"480d04bbaa3215a9cbf2e55747258cb665cd4c5f","tid":2208246,"uid":70485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"前政務司司長陳方安生在美國獲頒國際人權獎，她在致辭時表示，對香港近年發展感到憂慮，形容香港已由「法治」演變成「以法而治」。<br />\n<br />\n政府晚上發出聲明回應有關言論，稱政府一直尊重及維護香港居民依法享有的權利，包括選舉權和被選舉權。但表示政府有責任執行和維護《基本法》，以及確保所有選舉均在符合《基本法》和相關選舉法律下進行。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中更表示，「任意發表貶低香港良好法治聲譽，並可能對法治社會造成損害的剛愎言論，對香港發展毫無助益。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n@ 2018-02-11 22:17 <br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/159103/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E9%99%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%89%E7%94%9F-%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%BB-%E8%B2%B6%E4%BD%8E%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F159103%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%2581%25B2%25E8%25AD%25BD%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%258A&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=0dd769d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/159103/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E9%99%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%89%E7%94%9F-%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%BB-%E8%B2%B6%E4%BD%8E%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E8%81%B2%E8%AD%BD%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%8A</a><br />\n<br />\nRef 2: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia